  "description": "## Deep Component Audit — hx-split-panel\n\n**Component directory:** `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-split-panel/`\n\n### wc-mcp Tools — USE THESE\n- `score_component`, `get_component`, `analyze_accessibility`, `list_css_parts`, `list_events`, `list_slots`, `get_design_tokens`\n- **Report wc-mcp bugs to `/Volumes/Development/booked/wc-tools` board.**\n\n### Audit Scope\n1. **Design Tokens** — `--hx-` tokens. Divider color, handle, min sizes. Dark mode.\n2. **Accessibility** — WCAG 2.1 AA. Separator role. Keyboard resize (arrow keys). aria-valuenow for position.\n3. **Functionality** — Horizontal/vertical. Drag to resize. Min/max panel sizes. Snap positions. Collapse. Initial position.\n4. **TypeScript** — Strict. No `any`.\n5. **CSS/Styling** — Shadow DOM. CSS Parts (divider, handle). Cursor styles. Responsive.\n6. **CEM Accuracy** — All API documented.\n7. **Tests** — 80%+ coverage. Drag. Keyboard resize. Min/max. Collapse. Snap.\n8. **Storybook** — Horizontal/vertical. Collapsible. Nested. With content.\n9. **Drupal Compatibility** — Layout tool. Twig-friendly.\n10. **Portability** — CDN-ready.\n\n### Deliverable\nDetailed audit report. Fix CRITICAL+HIGH. Document rest.",
